description:
The original and official promo video for the single "The Number One Song In Heaven" from the 1979 album No. 1 In Heaven.

No. 1 In Heaven • 40th Anniversary Edition is released March 2019 on double LP/CD. Available for pre-order → http://store.allsparks.com
